# FGN Fine Gold Nation Landing Page - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview

This is a React TypeScript landing page for FGN Fine Gold Nation with English/Mongolian localization and Motion animations.

## Coding Standards

### General

- Use TypeScript for all files
- Use functional components with hooks
- Follow React best practices
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Implement responsive design (mobile-first)
- Use Motion library for animations

### File Naming

- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `Header.tsx`, `HeroSection.tsx`)
- Utilities: camelCase (e.g., `useLocalization.ts`, `animationUtils.ts`)
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (e.g., `TRANSLATION_KEYS.ts`)

### Component Structure

```typescript
// Component template
interface ComponentProps {
  // props here
}

export const Component: React.FC<ComponentProps> = ({ prop1, prop2 }) => {
  // hooks here

  return (
    // JSX here
  );
};
```

### Styling Guidelines

- Use Tailwind CSS classes
- Create custom CSS only when necessary
- Use CSS variables for design tokens
- Implement dark theme support
- Ensure accessibility (ARIA labels, keyboard navigation)

### Animation Guidelines

- Use Motion library for all animations
- Implement smooth transitions
- Support reduced motion preferences
- Optimize for performance
- Use scroll-triggered animations

### Localization

- Use i18next for translations
- Support English (en) and Mongolian (mn)
- Implement automatic language detection
- Store language preference in localStorage
- Handle RTL text for Mongolian

### Performance

- Lazy load components when possible
- Optimize images and assets
- Use React.memo for expensive components
- Implement proper loading states

### Accessibility

- Use semantic HTML
- Add proper ARIA labels
- Ensure keyboard navigation
- Support screen readers
- Test with accessibility tools

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── common/          # Reusable UI components
│   ├── layout/          # Layout components
│   └── sections/        # Page sections
├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks
├── locales/             # Translation files
│   ├── en/
│   └── mn/
├── types/               # TypeScript type definitions
├── utils/               # Utility functions
├── animations/          # Animation configurations
└── assets/              # Images, fonts, etc.
```

## Key Features to Implement

1. Responsive design with mobile-first approach
2. English/Mongolian localization with auto-detection
3. Smooth animations using Motion library
4. Golden gradient design elements
5. Professional financial services aesthetic
6. SEO and accessibility compliance

## Dependencies

- React 18+
- TypeScript 5+
- Tailwind CSS 3+
- Motion library
- i18next + react-i18next
- Vite build tool

## Code Quality

- Use Prettier for formatting
- Use ESLint for linting
- Follow TypeScript strict mode
- Write clean, readable code
- Add proper comments for complex logic
